Running this example
====================

1.  Open a console.

2.  Run

        rackup rubycas_server.ru

3.  Open a console.

4.  Run

        rackup cas_proxy_callback.ru

5.  Open a console.

6.  Run

        rackup fortune_server.ru

7.  Open a console.

8.  Run

        ruby -rubygems fortune_client.rb

9.  Open a Web browser.

10. Go to

        http://localhost:4567

11. Enter the login details

        mr296 / br0wn

12. Log in.

13. Play around.
